          "type": "text",
          "text": "Published.TemporalAccountLevelSummaryByCityWide",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table. It ensures that only the latest billing period can be removed, preventing accidental deletion of older periods. The procedure also updates the "
